INSERT INTO `educations` VALUES (85, 955, 'B.Sc ', 'graduate', 'Science', '1985-04-01', '1988-03-31', 'I have experience in counseling students to study further for higher education abroad. I am working with a student who wants to pursue a Doctoral degree in any European country.\nI have been a qualified teacher and an academic counselor for the past year because I have the skills you need and the experience to back them up. I saw your advertisement and thought this would be a perfect opportunity for me. Your advertisement is a career move for me. I am confident that I am a good fit for this position for several reasons, precisely because of my dedication to going above and beyond in a job. I am committed to learning any skill to succeed in this role. For example, I updated myself on various platforms for my previous job by reading blogs, listening to the news, and listening to debates. Upgradation allowed me to incorporate myself into my marketing role, cutting down on expenses for Biology (NEET). Presently, I teach English to various CBSE BOARD & IGCSE Board classes. I have done Post Post-Graduation in Education. I updated myself on my successful completion of the CTET exam. I also prepare students for the NEET Preparation (Biology & Chemistry). In my previous job, I worked as an Academic Supervisor. My hard work enables me to work with you in Science/Chemistry/Biology/Botany/Zoology/English. I know you are seeking a self-motivated individual for this job, and I am that candidate. This is because I was having a wonderful experience working as a TGT (Science). Presently, I am working in an NGO, Prayas at Noida, as a Support Coordinator and teaching classes IX & X. Presently, I am doing a Content writing course from IIM Skills for my personal growth. I have 15 years of Primary & Secondary teaching experience in various positions like Academic Supervisor, Activity Coordinator, Admission Coordinator, etc. I am an international online teaching student of the GCSE Board student of Singapore. I have relevant experience in international teaching. I have also worked with the Trendzhits website.\n\n\n\n', 'A', '2025-10-05 06:43:02', '2025-10-05 06:43:02');
